@startuml
title "UC-09: Manage Inventory & Promotions"

actor Manager
participant "Mr. Daebak System" as System

== View Inventory ==
Manager -> System: 1. Request inventory status
activate System
System --> Manager: 2. Inventory list\n(ingredients, quantities, low-stock alerts)
deactivate System

== Adjust Stock ==
Manager -> System: 3. Update stock quantity\n(ingredient_id, quantity_change)
activate System
System --> Manager: 4. Stock updated successfully
deactivate System

== Manage Promotions ==
Manager -> System: 5. Request promotion list
activate System
System --> Manager: 6. Event/promotion list
deactivate System

Manager -> System: 7. Create/Update promotion\n(title, period, discount details)
activate System
System --> Manager: 8. Promotion saved successfully
deactivate System

@enduml
